title: If You Can Dream It, You Can Do It
description:
In this episode, Jessi and Stew hang out with Emily Buckley who owns Willow Salon in Arizona. She has been our online friend for years and it was so fun chatting with her! We talk salon ownership, balancing responsibilities, following your dreams and more.
